00:24:47,200 --> 00:24:48,920
[SPEAKER_00] Kad mi dođu na ispred, kad mi dođu u razgovor.

321
00:24:48,920 --> 00:24:51,480
[SPEAKER_00] Znate, kad mi muž dođe, prevara.

322
00:24:51,480 --> 00:24:52,579
