328
00:25:00,420 --> 00:25:01,779
[SPEAKER_00] Pa reci, šta je, šta je prijeto?

329
00:25:01,779 --> 00:25:02,059
[SPEAKER_00] Reci.

330
00:25:02,059 --> 00:25:03,619
[SPEAKER_00] Pa, znaš šta?

331
00:25:03,619 --> 00:25:07,299
