337
00:25:17,539 --> 00:25:20,140
[SPEAKER_00] Ja rekao, pa kako to prijatelju?

338
00:25:20,140 --> 00:25:22,660
[SPEAKER_00] Ja vidim stvarno suze.

339
00:25:22,660 --> 00:25:24,180
[SPEAKER_00] I stvarno osjećaj krivnje.

340
00:25:25,900 --> 00:25:26,480
[SPEAKER_00] I znate šta?

341
